Package ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.model.user.group

Class UserGroupJoin

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.model.user.group.UserGroupJoin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IridaThing, Join<User,​UserGroup>, Timestamped<java.lang.Long>
    @Entity
public final class UserGroupJoin
extends java.lang.Object
implements Join<User,​UserGroup>
    A relationship between an individual User account and a UserGroup. This class closely mirrors the ProjectUserJoin in that a UserGroup is assigned a level of access using the ProjectRole enum.
    See Also:
    ProjectUserJoin, ProjectRole
